# Keeps coredist/ present so tauri.conf's `resources` glob always matches (dev +
# cargo builds work with no staged core). tools/build-release.ps1 stages
# latch.exe here for release bundles; it installs into <install>/coredist/ next
# to the GUI exe, where tools.rs resolves it. (ffmpeg/yt-dlp are self-provisioned
# at runtime, not bundled.)
